column5: Building F is located next to the football field and the Satya Wacana Christian University Faculty of Languages ??and Arts (FBS) building. Building F is also a building used for lectures and offices for the Faculty of Law, Satya Wacana Christian University (UKSW). 5 floors with the following functions: Floors 1-3 are used for lectures Floors 4-5 are used for offices for the Law Faculty and its staff, both lecturers and non-lecturer staff. On the 1st floor there are room guards and keys for each room in building F.
